sundowner
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a dog reluctant to work in hot sunny conditions [ preferring to lie in the shade or in a water-trough. ]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:sooner
Pronunciation:
Notes:
